## Limitations

The report is based on available online resources and may not encompass all aspects of the impact of abusive parenting on child development. Some sources may not be up-to-date, and the findings are limited to the information provided by the selected articles. Further research, including longitudinal studies, would provide a more comprehensive understanding of the long-term effects of child abuse.

